{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "本章题为\"宴无好宴\"，宫素素设宴款待牛肉汤与西门吹雪，席间宫萍突然刺杀西门吹雪，被一剑击倒。随后沙大户、老板娘、杂货店老板、黄小虫、赵瞎子等人相继登场，围绕陆小凤之死展开激烈争论。西门吹雪冷静指认黄石镇在场的每一个人——沙大户、老板、老板娘、赵瞎子、黄小虫乃至宫素素——都是杀害陆小凤的凶手。宫素素随即承认酒中有毒，众人纷纷得意发笑，西门吹雪与牛肉汤先后中毒倒下。与此同时，远在酒楼的小老头与小老太婆商议是否赶往黄石镇，小老太婆担心西门吹雪遇害，提及柳如钢与陆小凤均死于黄石镇，最终小老头决定动身前往。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "你知道陆小凤的死因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "那么好的人，为什么偏偏那么早死呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "是谁杀他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "陆小凤是我最仰慕的人，居然死在黄石镇上，我实在难过极了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "讲难过，最难过的应该是我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "难道你不知道我和他的关系？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "你快告诉我，是谁杀的？我一定要替他报仇。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "谁杀的？谁能杀得了陆小凤？能杀他的人，当然是他最亲近的人，是他最不会提防的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_su_su",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你马上就知道了。我已经派人去把这些人找来，他们还没来以前，我们为什么不多喝两杯，遥祝陆大侠在天之灵？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "宫萍，你想干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "我听说西门公子的剑术已经练到无剑的境界，我想领教一下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "哼！我看你是活得不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "拔剑吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "我看你真的是活得不耐烦了，",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你居然敢叫西门大侠拔剑，你知道他一拔剑的后果吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_gong_ping",
      "text": "你死定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "宫萍",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "每件事都有例外的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑法！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_da_hu",
      "speaker_name": "沙大户",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西门吹雪无剑的境界，果然名不虚传。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "杂货店老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实，我早就知道谁是凶手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ban_niang",
      "speaker_name": "老板娘",
      "listener": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "text": "他根本就不知道谁是凶手。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "杂货店老板",
      "listener": "char_lao_ban_niang",
      "text": "你为什么认为我不知道谁是凶手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ban_niang",
      "speaker_name": "老板娘",
      "listener": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "text": "你如果知道，你会不早说吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "杂货店老板",
      "listener": "char_lao_ban_niang",
      "text": "早说？早说出来，我会活到现在吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "speaker_name": "黄小虫",
      "listener": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "text": "你不怕凶手杀你灭口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_za_huo_dian_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "杂货店老板",
      "listener": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "text": "杀我灭口？那他岂不自己暴露身份？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到底谁是凶手？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "赵瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好凶手是很多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "speaker_name": "黄小虫",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "赵瞎子",
      "listener": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "text": "为什么？凶手愈多，我的棺材生意不就愈好吗？哈哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶手是很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "还有？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "西门吹雪，你猜对了。黄石镇上的每一个人，都是杀死陆小凤的凶手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ban_niang",
      "speaker_name": "老板娘",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "只可惜，你知道得太迟了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "赵瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不，一点也不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "speaker_name": "黄小虫",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "text": "为什么不迟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "赵瞎子",
      "listener": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "text": "因为刚好来得及睡我的棺材。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你想问，酒里是不是有毒，对不对？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "宫素素",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我告诉你，酒里有毒。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "speaker_name": "黄小虫",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你现在是不是愈来愈看不清楚面前的东西？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_xiao_chong",
      "speaker_name": "黄小虫",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你还得意得了吗？你还有没有西门大侠的什么话，要告诉我们？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "你现在就去黄石镇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "现在不去，什么时候才去？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "当然等一切情况都明了的时候才去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "我怕太迟了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "怎么会太迟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "到时案子破了，我的小朋友却也许被害了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "西门吹雪会被害？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "他会被害？你说些新鲜一点的笑话可以吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "你觉得这很好笑吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "你不觉得好笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "一点也不。你别忘了，柳如钢死在黄石镇，陆小凤也死在黄石镇。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "小老太婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "干什么？去黄石镇呀。",
